Why I reject CD 1 (greatest‑hits collection)
- Lack of clear analogue/tape emphasis: While CD 1 offers close‑mic, lyric‑forward mixes and preserves micro‑dynamics, it is described primarily as a polished greatest‑hits collection with mastering that “increases presence.” The description does not emphasize analogue remastering or tape warmth. Given my explicit preference for analogue warmth and tape‑forward sonics, CD 2’s stated uncompressed analogue remaster is a closer, more specific match.
